In one of these direct access to kernel driver is used (without libasound):
  git clone https://github.com/swetland/alsa
  git clone https://github.com/ikle/test-alsa
  git clone https://github.com/robpennock/pi_guitar

To use play.w on desktop, device must be specified as "sysdefault:CARD=Intel" (see "aplay -L")

Read http://www.volkerschatz.com/noise/alsa.html
